org.lafayette.server
Class Registry

java.lang.Object
  org.lafayette.server.Registry

public final class Registry
extends Object

Registers shared core resources. Shared resources:

  • version
  • stage
  • database connection
  • server configuration
All resources are initialized with default values so the registry never returns null.

Author:
Sven Strittmatter
